    "body": "Hi there @djenning90! Have you looked at our [`TokenVesting`](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/v2.1.3/contracts/drafts/TokenVesting.sol) contract? It decouples the token from the vesting, so that there are no restrictions placed upon it, which I think is pretty neat (considering the vesting period should be short-lived when compared to the actual token usage).\r\n\r\nWe're also gathering feedback regarding vesting scheme requirements, since that contract isn't flexible enough to account for some real-life scenarios: read [here](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/issues/1214) for some initial ideas, and share your feedback!",
